dct_title_s: Oil & gas map of Mexico / Petroleum Economist Cartographic ; produced by the Petroleum Economist, a division of Euromoney Global Limited in association with PEMEX ; designed by K. Fuller and P. Bush.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown shading. Depth shown by shading. Shows gas fields, oil fields, gas pipelines, oil pipelines, liquefied natural gas import terminals, refineries, and tanker terminals. Includes statistical tables and graphs. "©The Petroleum Economist Limited, London, September 2015." "Published September 2015"
